<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ض ن ك<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣١٤٥ - ض ن ك]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ضنَكَ يَضنُك، ضَنْكًا، فهو ضانِك، والمفعول مَضْنوك<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ضنَك اللهُ رزقَه:</span> ضيَّقَه عليه <span class="c1">"عانى من ضَنْك عيشه"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>